desc: True if changes have been made to {@link #loadedChunks} and thus a new copy of the collection has to be made into {@link #immutableLoadedChunks}.

name: tickingFuture
desc: A future that returns the chunk if it is a ticking chunk, {@link net.minecraft.world.server.ChunkHolder.IChunkLoadingError#UNLOADED} otherwise.

name: entityTickingFuture
desc: A future that returns the chunk if it is an entity ticking chunk, {@link net.minecraft.world.server.ChunkHolder.IChunkLoadingError#UNLOADED} otherwise.

name: isLoadingStart
desc: Set to {@code true} when the crossbow is 20% charged.

name: isLoadingMiddle
desc: Set to {@code true} when the crossbow is 50% charged.

name: targetEntitySelector
desc: This filter is applied to the Entity search. Only matching entities will be targeted.

name: flagGoals
desc: Goals currently using a particular flag

name: specificItems
desc: Defines items villagers of this profession can pick up and use.

name: relatedWorldBlocks
desc: World blocks this profession interracts with.

name: potionStack
desc: An ItemStack that can have potion effects written to it.

name: food
desc: Sets food information to this item

name: buyingStackFirst
desc: The first input for this offer.

name: buyingStackSecond
desc: The second input for this offer.

name: sellingStack
desc: The output of this offer.

name: SENTINEL
desc: Value representing an absent or invalid chunkpos

name: lootTable
desc: Sets loot table information

name: borderFuture
desc: A future that returns the chunk if it is a border chunk, {@link net.minecraft.world.server.ChunkHolder.IChunkLoadingError#UNLOADED} otherwise.

name: chunksToRetain
desc: Section column positions (section positions with Y=0) that need to be kept even if some of their sections could otherwise be removed.

name: entriesRunThisTick
desc: Entries from {@link #pendingTickListEntriesThisTick} that have already run this tick.

name: guiScreenServer
desc: The screen to display when OK is clicked on the disconnect screen.\n \nSeems to be either null (integrated server) or an instance of either {@link MultiplayerScreen} (when connecting to a server) or {@link com.mojang.realmsclient.gui.screens.RealmsTermsScreen} (when connecting to MCO server)

name: LOGGER
desc: Unused (probably related to the unused parameter in the constructor)

name: probability
desc: Probability to generate a beehive

name: headChild
desc: Added as a result/workaround for the loss of renderWithRotation

name: tailChild
desc: Added as a result/workaround for the loss of renderWithRotation

name: hashedSeed
desc: First 8 bytes of the SHA-256 hash of the world's seed

name: enableRespawnScreen
desc: Set to false when the doImmediateRespawn gamerule is true

name: hashedSeed
desc: First 8 bytes of the SHA-256 hash of the world's seed

name: updateLCG
desc: Contains the current Linear Congruential Generator seed for block updates. Used with an A value of 3 and a C value of 0x3c6ef35f, producing a highly planar series of values ill-suited for choosing random blocks in a 16x128x16 field.

name: goalOwner
desc: The entity that this goal belongs to

name: color
desc: The color index used to draw the blocks of this material on maps.

name: pushReaction
desc: Mobility information flag. 0 indicates that this block is normal, 1 indicates that it can't push other blocks, 2 indicates that it can't be pushed.

name: COLORS
desc: Holds all the 16 colors used on maps, very similar of a pallete system.

name: cachedEntity
desc: Cached instance of the entity to render inside the spawner.
